        "content": "The final CoinJoin TX is a standard SegWit v0 transaction:\n\n  nVersion (4B)\n  Marker + Flag (SegWit signal)\n  2 inputs — empty scriptSig, witness spends\n  2 equal-value outputs\n  witness[0] = Alice sig + pubkey\n  witness[1] = Bob sig + pubkey\n  nLocktime (4B)\n\nBoth inputs are verified independently using script_verification. Each check confirms the signature matches the scriptPubKey — without requiring the other participant's key.",
